Colour (Figure 12
A-C
). Specimens in life with body black/brownish black; paraterga white/yellowish white/whitish yellow; antennae (except whitish distal part of antennomeres 7 and 8) and metaterga (posterior part) brown/brownish black; head and collum brown/blackish brown; prozona and metaterga (anterior part) black; surface below paraterga black/brownish black; sterna and epiproct brown; legs brown/pale brown; a few basal podomeres pale whitish brown.
